     H            Y.
     F** EJKR51 ************************************
     F* B2B_S  GET PARTNER GROUP AND ID            *
     F* T.SAKAKI          2016.11.12               *
     F********************************** EDIR55 ****
     FEJKPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     I*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIME
     I                                        1   60@@TIME
     I                                        7  140@@DATE
     I*
     IINFDSP     SDS
     I                                        1  10 PGMNM
     I                                      254 263 USID
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   ENTRY LIST                                       *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C* IN
     C                     PARM           P@NONY  4         DETAIL CODE
     C                     PARM           P@SNRV  1         SEND OR RECEIVE
     C                     PARM           P@DKBN  3         EDI DATA CODE
     C* OUT
     C                     PARM           P@JYKB  2         PARTNER GROUP.
     C                     PARM           P@PTID 12         PARTNER ID.
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   MAIN ROUTINE                                     *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     TIME           @TIME
     C*
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@JYKB
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@PTID
     C*
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           P@NONY
     C                     KFLD           P@SNRV
     C                     KFLD           P@DKBN
     C*
     C           KEY1      CHAINEJKPL12              85
     C           *IN85     IFEQ '0'
     C           DPSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELDPJSYS    P@JYKB
     C                     MOVELDPPTID    P@PTID
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
